member.example:
This sample shows how to call GetArrayBasicsAsync and parse the result.

var client = new ArrayBasicClient();

Response response = await client.GetArrayBasicsAsync();

JsonElement result = JsonDocument.Parse(response.ContentStream).RootElement;
Console.WriteLine(result[0].GetProperty("name").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result[0].GetProperty("age").ToString());

This sample shows how to call GetArrayBasicsAsync with all parameters, and how to parse the result.

var client = new ArrayBasicClient();

Response response = await client.GetArrayBasicsAsync("<nextLink>");

JsonElement result = JsonDocument.Parse(response.ContentStream).RootElement;
Console.WriteLine(result[0].GetProperty("name").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result[0].GetProperty("tag").ToString());
Console.WriteLine(result[0].GetProperty("age").ToString());

